structure.unit: STOCK INSURANCE COMPANIES -- OTHER THAN LIFE (Superseded)

law.history: Repealed 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 21, sec. 2. -- Created 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 154, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Insurance relating to highway contracts to be written only by licensed resident agents; commissions not to be divided.
